name: Bitget Celebrates Tokenized Stocks Surpass $500M in Spot Volume With Extension of Zero-Fee Promotion
description: The weathered Saint of Protocol lifts the volumetric core, a sacred $500M weight. Tungsten resonance confirms the circuit's fidelity as iridescent cyan bleeds onto the broken floor, sustaining the zero-fee entropy required for global equity flow.
